tagline: My Nokia Blog client for Sailfish Os
body:
### Welcome to the project page for My Nokia Blog's Sailfish Client.
This page will host information about the app, revisions I have made, feature list, and also possibly a place not only to get feedback, but to list bugs that users have come across.

###Support
Get in touch with me either on;
